Installation
============

* Register a new app at http://soundcloud.com/you/apps/new. Set the callback URL
  to http://<host>/auth/soundcloud.
* Copy the values for 'Client ID' and 'Client Secret' to the appropriate keys in
  config/config.yml (check config.yml.sample).
* Create a user at soundcloud. All interaction with soundcloud will happen
  through this user.
* Copy the user's email and password to the appropriate keys in
  config/config.yml (check config.yml.sample).
* ???
* Profit!